Token.Abstract: BKDeltaCalculator takes two arrays as input and outputs a dictionary with the following keys:
Resolve differences between two versions of an array.

Parameter.Name: oldArray
Parameter.Abstract: the array representing the "old" version of the array

Parameter.Name: newArray
Parameter.Abstract: the array representing the "new" version of the array.

ReturnValue.Abstract: A dictionary containing NSIndexSets representing added, moved, removed, and unchanged elements.
